    <topic>Control Type</topic>
    <description>The Control type property can be used to change the type of a Data control to any other Data control type, including Add-in controls (found in the 'More...' option in the Data Controls toolbox.)</description>
    <discussion>
        <p>The Control type can be changed for any Data control to one of the following by editing the control's *[ui:Control Type]* property.</p>
    </discussion>
