        <section>
            <description>
                <p>In addition, all Add-in controls (which can be viewed by clicking "*[ui:More...]*" in the Data Controls toolbox) are also available in the *[ui:Control Type]* options. Both the add-in controls shipped with Alpha Anywhere and any [add-in controls that you create yourself] will be included.</p>
